data.description: All you could want in a home!!! Space, quality, location! Get ready to call this 5+ bed, three bath, three stall garage HOME. Let's start with the garage space: epoxied floors, storage cabinets, floor drains, ceiling fan, ventilation system (exactly what you need to make year-round grilling and smoking enjoyable!), sheetrocked, heated, a roll down screen door to keep the mosquitos out, and steel kick plate around the interior of the garage. Leading into the house from the garage you will find a large closet and ample room for a table or bench in the oversized split foyer. Natural light floods your upper level where you will find luxury vinyl flooring in your living, dining and kitchen space. Exit through the sliding door in the dining area to a 12 x 16 back deck overlooking your fully fenced backyard complete with sprinklers, concrete curbing and a shed. The tasteful kitchen contains subway tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Find three of the five bedrooms and two of the bathrooms on the upper floor, including a master ensuite. The daylight lower level provides two more bedrooms plus a bonus room that could easily serve as a sixth bedroom, another bath, large laundry room and a family room that spans the entire width of the house. Enjoy morning coffee and evening wine on your stamped concrete front patio and covered front porch. All details have been tended to as the home contains a whole house humidifier and a security system. What are you waiting for?! Call your agent today for a private showing!!
